@giàn giụa
- Overflow profusely
=Nước mắt giàn giụa+her tears overflowed profusely; she was bathed in tears; her eyes were profusely overflowing with tears

[giàn giụa] to overflow profusely. 
 Đôi má nàng giàn giụa nước mắt 
 Her tears overflowed profusely; 
 She was bathed in tears; 
 Her cheeks were bathed in tears; 
 Her cheeks were streaming with tears

@già cả
